<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>805</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>yào jǐng xǐng 迦南805</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 suǒ yǐ nǐ men yào jǐng xǐng, yīn wèi nǐ men bù zhī dào
 jiā zhǔ shén me shí hòu lái. huò wǎn shàng huò bàn yè huò jī jiào,
 kǒng pà tā hū rán lái dào. kàn jiàn nǐ men shuì zhe le.
 zhǔ duì wǒ men shuō de huà, qiān wàn yào jì láo.
 shuō huà xíng shì xiǎo xīn jǐn shèn, zǒng yào chá yàn ràng shén guāng zhào.
 kǒng pà jiā zhǔ hū rán lái dào, xiàn zài yào jǐng xǐng dǎo gào.</lyrics>
</song>